title: Piston Duke makes it's entry to the MSFS marketplace
description:
A new developer has entered the marketplace Black Square and they are directly adding 2 aircrafts to the marketplace. The first one is the Piston Duke comes with a very complete cockpit including an EFB which allows you to configure multiple settings and even failures. The aircraft comes with a 160 pages thick manual so it is pretty complete.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
